# Copy the image over

_WFCAM_HELLO_

# Display it

_DISPLAY_IMAGE_

=head1 NAME

QUICK_LOOK -- Simply copy and display an image

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe does the usual copy of an input image and just displays it

=head1 NOTES

None

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

None

=head1 CONFIGURABLE STEERING PARAMETERS

None

=head1 IMPLEMENTATION STATUS

=over 4

=item *

All processing is done with CIRDR routines.

=item *

Files are in standard Multi-extension FITS.

=back

